createDeck(int) - Method in class deck.CharacterDeckCreator
This method effects an Overloading and allows to create a new object deck.CharacterDeck and then to populate it in order to the specific number of Player: - if numberPlayer is an even number then the number of HumanCards are equals to the number of AlienCards - if numberPlayer is an odd number then the number of AlienCards in will exceed the number of HumanCards by one.
